sequenceDiagram

participant User
participant Device
participant AD as On-Prem AD
participant AADConnect
participant Entra as Azure Entra ID
participant MFA
participant CA as Conditional Access
participant PIM
participant Resource as Cloud Resource

Note over AD,AADConnect: Identity Synchronization
AD->>AADConnect: Sync users, groups, password hash
AADConnect->>Entra: Update cloud identity directory

Note over User,Resource: Authentication Flow

User->>Device: Login Request
Device->>Entra: Authentication Request

Entra->>CA: Evaluate Policy

CA->>MFA: Require MFA
MFA->>User: Push/OTP Verification
User->>MFA: Approves MFA

MFA->>Entra: Authentication Success

Note over Entra,PIM: Privileged Access Flow

User->>PIM: Request Role Activation
PIM->>MFA: Step-Up Authentication
PIM->>Entra: Issue Privileged Token

Entra->>Resource: Access Token Issued
Resource->>User: Authorized Access
